document_data.name: The Lady's Sheaves
document_data.mainbody: The '''Lady's Sheaves''' was a [[Chauntea|Chauntean]] temple in the city-state of [[Saelmur]].
document_data.Location: This temple situated close to the Central Marketplace of Saelmur.
document_data.Inhabitants: In the mid-to-late 14{{th}} century [[DR]], the clergy of the Lady's Sheaves was led by [[Thera Goldencorn]].
